              </div>
              <p class="mt-0.5 font-body text-xs text-white/50">Founder of progsu</p>
              <div class="mt-2.5 border-t border-white/8 pt-2.5">
                <p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70">Started progsu 7 months ago, putting in $6k total out of pocket. We spent 4 weeks planning, pitching, and organizing Hacklanta as GSU's first hackathon.</p>
