              <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/joeyzhangdev/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="rounded border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-2 text-white/50 transition-all hover:border-white/25 hover:bg-white/10 hover:text-white" aria-label="LinkedIn">
